**LIX calculator:** https://spraakbanken.gu.se/verktyg/lix/

**Number of words:** 62
**Number of long words (more than 6 letters):** 17
**Number of sentences:** 5

**LIX formula:** LIX = (number of words / number of sentences) + (number of long words / number of sentences)

**LIX calculation:**
((62 / 5) + (17 / 5)) = 12.4 + 3.4 = 15.8

**LIX result:**
LIX = 15.8